One of the best parts of Pongal is the Kummi dance! The elegant steps, the music, people celebrating. It’s the whole package that works out! Another beautiful aspect of doing the Kummi is the way my braid sways with me, elegant, strong and beautiful!
Naturally, I take good care of it and I trust no one but @dove Hair fall Rescue Shampoo and Conditioner for it. Nothing but the best for my hair. After all, #EnPinnalEnPride! ☺️

#Ad
Bhogi Pongal is all about discarding the old and welcoming the new year with renewed spirits! And this Pongal I am ready to discard some negativity and approach the new year with strength and beauty! Just like my braid with @dove Hair fall Rescue Shampoo and Conditioner! 
I am all ready to bring in the Pongal celebrations and make sure my pinnal is ready too. After all, #EnPinnalEnPride!
